.org/web/20190723053812/https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-crime/article/1910845/shots-fired-and-bricks-thrown-hong-kong-tense-after-mong |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="法新社 01">{{Cite web |url = https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jun/11/hong-kong-jails-independence-leader-edward-leung-for-six-years |title = Hong Kong jails independence leader Edward Leung for six years |author = [[法新社|法新社]] |date = 2018-06-11 |publisher = 《[[衛報|衛報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723053801/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jun/11/hong-kong-jails-independence-leader-edward-leung-for-six-years |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。為了在現場保護市民，梁天琦在[[騷亂|騷亂]]期間宣布進行競選遊行<ref name = "立場新聞 05"/>，拒絕離開<ref name="香港商業電台 01">{{Cite web |url = https://hk.news.yahoo.com/本土民主前線稱梁天琦被捕-000200599.html |title = 本土民主前線稱梁天琦被捕 |author = [[香港商業電台|香港商業電台]] |date = 2016-02-09 |publisher = {{Link-en|雅虎新聞|Yahoo! News}} |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723111146/https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2590%25A6%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-000200599.html |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。大批市民聚集在旺角街頭，並在[[彌敦道|彌敦道]]縱火，與鎮暴警察對峙<ref name = "蘋果日報 04"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/6474/旺角黑夜-激戰-有人在彌敦道縱火-多名警員示威者跌倒 |title = 【旺角黑夜：激戰】有人在彌敦道縱火　多名警員示威者跌倒 |author = 陳永武和梁融軒 |date = 2016-02-09 |publisher = [[香港01|香港01]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723111155/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/6474/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E9%BB%91%E5%A4%9C-%E6%BF%80%E6%88%B0-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%9C%A8%E5%BD%8C%E6%95%A6%E9%81%93%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB-%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%