新聞 02"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.hongkongfp.com/2016/07/26/election-officials-email-more-pro-independence-legco-candidates-asking-about-political-stance/ |title = Election officials email more pro-independence LegCo candidates asking about political stance |author = Kris Cheng |date = 2016-07-26 |publisher = [[香港自由新聞|香港自由新聞]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723093745/https://www.hongkongfp.com/2016/07/26/election-officials-email-more-pro-independence-legco-candidates-asking-about-political-stance/ |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Kris Cheng 01">{{Cite web |url = https://www.hongkongfp.com/2016/08/02/edward-leung-not-genuinely-switched-pro-independence-stance-says-election-official/ |title = Edward Leung has not genuinely switched from pro-independence stance, says election official |author = Kris Cheng |date = 2016-08-02 |publisher = [[香港自由新聞|香港自由新聞]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190722061142/https://www.hongkongfp.com/2016/08/02/edward-leung-not-genuinely-switched-pro-independence-stance-says-election-official/ |archive-date = 2019-07-22 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

