=4h |title = 梁天琦斥被挑釁 左報狗仔隊晚上先發制人報警稱被襲 |author =  |date = 2016-08-14 |publisher = 《[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  }}</ref>。

在這期間，《大公報》還持續報導梁天琦的背景，並派遣記者前往他在湖北省武漢市的出生地，調查祖屋等成長資料<ref name = "施文達 01"/><ref name = "施文達 02"/>。同年9月，他和黃台仰參加在[[比利時|比利時]][[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]]舉行的「第7屆聲援西藏組織網絡大會」，與旅居美國的維權律師[[陳光誠|陳光誠]]交流<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1830063 |title = 港獨、藏獨合流？港媒如此觀察… |author =  |date = 2016-08-14 |publisher = 《[[自由時報|自由時報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190623123708/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1830063 |archive-date = 2019-06-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。他還曾經在電臺節目表示，等到選舉結果刊載至《[[香港政府憲報|香港政府憲報]]》後，將會提出[[選舉呈請|選舉呈請]]<ref name = "立場新聞 03"/>。到了10月7日，他就選舉資格遭到取消提出選舉呈請<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2026069/hong-kong-independence-advocate-edward-leung-files-legal |title = Hong Kong independence advocate Edward Leung files legal petition over Legco elections ban |author = Eddie Lee |date = 2016-10-07 |publisher = 《[[南華早報|南華早報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723070213/https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2026069/hong-kong-independence-advocate-edward-leung-files-legal |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

另一方面，在旺角騷亂結束後，梁天琦被控兩項參與暴動罪和一項煽動暴動罪，轉往香港特別行政區高等法院審理<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160629/19674333 |title = 旺角騷亂　黃台仰梁天琦轉高院審 |author = 勞東來和羅日昇 |date = 2016-06-29 |publisher = 《[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723111150/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20160629/19674333 |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。2017年12月18日，在被指控涉嫌參與暴動等罪名後，本土民主前線發表聲明，宣布發言人梁天琦希望在審訊前數個月陪伴親人，已經辭退黨籍與發言人職務<ref name = "蘋果日報 03"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.mingpao.com/pns/港聞/article/20171219/s00002/1513620709701/梁天琦退出本民前-青政否認戰補選 |title = 梁天琦退出本民前 青政否認戰補選 |author =  |date = 2017-12-19 |publisher = 《[[明報|明報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723093036/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E/article/20171219/s00002/1513620709701/%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2590%25A6%25E9%2580%2580%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2589%258D-%25E9%259D%2592%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%2588%25B0%25E8%25A3%259C%25E9%2581%25B8 |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。本土民主前線對此表示可惜，但尊重他的決定<ref name = "蘋果日報 03"/>。

== 罪成入獄 ==
[[File:香港旺角衝突案_法庭向黃台仰李東昇發拘捕令3.jpg|thumb]]，就第三度閉門預審應訊<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.voacantonese.com/a/hk-rioting-charges-issued-2-arrest-warrants-after-activists-failed-to-appear/4156576.html |title = 香港旺角衝突案 法庭向黃台仰李東昇發拘捕令 |author = 湯惠芸 |date = 2017-12-09 |publisher = [[美國之音|美國之音]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190724041920/https://www.voacantonese.com/a/hk-rioting-charges-issued-2-arrest-warrants-after-activists-failed-to-appear/4156576.html |archive-date = 2019-07-24 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。]]

2018年1月18日，梁天琦和其他5名抗議者因為在旺角騷亂中，涉嫌參與暴動罪而出庭<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-court-riot/hong-kong-pro-independence-protest-leader-appears-in-court-for-rioting-idUSKBN1F70ZJ |title = Hong Kong pro-independence protest leader appears in court for 'rioting' |author = Venus Wu |date = 2018-01-18 |publisher = [[路透社|路透社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723081906/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-court-riot/hong-kong-pro-independence-protest-leader-appears-in-court-for-rioting-idUSKBN1F70ZJ |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，梁天琦與黃台仰還被指控煽惑他人暴動<ref name = "蘇曉欣 01"/>。梁天琦、[[李諾文|李諾文]]、[[林傲軒|林傲軒]]與[[容偉業|容偉業]]共同面對一項暴動罪罪名──在2016年2月8日至2月9日期間，在旺角砵蘭街參與暴動<ref name = "黎彩燕 01"/><ref name="蘇曉欣 02">{{Cite web |url = https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190322/59397186 |title = 【旺角騷亂】重審梁天琦暴動罪名不成立 「美國隊長」三項罪成還柙 |author = 蘇曉欣、蔡少玲和鄭語霆 |date = 2019-03-25 |publisher = 《[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190623125517/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190322/59397186 |archive-date = 2019-06-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，梁天琦還被指控向準備制止手持磚頭人士的警員文錦璣，丟擲白色塑料瓶、腳踢、及以木製卡板打向背部，造成後者左膝、右後背、右膝、左耳等擦傷與觸痛，被判傷2%永久傷殘<ref name="明報 03">{{Cite web |url = https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20180122/s00001/1516597668045/【暴動罪審訊】梁天琦認襲警-黃家駒認暴動罪-即時還押 |title = 【暴動罪審訊】梁天琦認襲警　黃家駒認暴動罪　即時還押 |author =  |date = 2018-01-22 |publisher = 《[[明報|明報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723133353/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E/article/20180122/s00001/1516597668045/%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E8%25A8%258A%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A7%2592%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%258A%25BC |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2018年1月22日，在香港特別行政區高等法院接受審訊時，梁天琦承認一項[[襲警罪|襲警罪]]，但否認暴動及煽惑暴動等3罪，隨後即時還押<ref name = "明報 03"/>。5月18日，9人[[香港陪審團制度|陪審團]]在香港特別行政區高等法院一致裁定，梁天琦在亞皆老街參與暴動罪及襲警罪的罪名成立<ref name="明報 01">{{Cite web |url = https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190322/s00001/1553238427571/【暴動罪審訊】梁天琦砵蘭街暴動罪脫-仍須就一暴動一襲警罪服刑 |title = 【暴動罪審訊】梁天琦砵蘭街暴動罪脫　仍須就一暴動一襲警罪服刑 |author =  |date = 2019-03-22 |publisher = 《[[明報|明報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190327202125/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190322/s00001/1553238427571/%E3%80%90%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E5%AF%A9%E8%A8%8A%E3%80%91%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E7%A0%B5%E8%98%AD%E8%A1%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E8%84%AB-%E4%BB%8D%E9%A0%88%E5%B0%B1%E4%B8%80%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%80%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA%E6%9C%8D%E5%88%91 |archive-date = 2019-03-27 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="立場新聞 04">{{Cite web |url = https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁天琦獄中閱沙特劇作-無處可逃-準備修讀第二個學士學位/ |title = 梁天琦獄中閱沙特劇作《無處可逃》　準備修讀第二個學士學位 |author =  |date = 2018-07-05 |publisher = [[立場新聞|立場新聞]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180712101724/http://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E7%8D%84%E4%B8%AD%E9%96%B1%E6%B2%99%E7%89%B9%E5%8A%87%E4%BD%9C-%E7%84%A1%E8%99%95%E5%8F%AF%E9%80%83-%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E4%BF%AE%E8%AE%80%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%80%8B%E5%AD%B8%E5%A3%AB%E5%AD%B8%E4%BD%8D/ |archive-date = 2018-07-12 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-law-and-crime/article/2146806/hong-kong-pro-independence-activist-edward |title = Hong Kong independence activist Edward Leung found guilty of rioting but cleared of incitement over Mong Kok unrest |author = Chris Lau和Jasmine Siu |date = 2018-05-18 |publisher = 《[[南華早報|南華早報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723093054/https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-law-and-crime/article/2146806/hong-kong-pro-independence-activist-edward |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，煽惑暴動罪則不成立<ref name = "蘇曉欣 01"/>。在得知判決後，他則表現平靜<ref name = "蘇曉欣 01"/>。6月11日，他因為在旺角騷亂中犯下暴動罪與襲警罪，被判處6年監禁<ref name = "法新社 01"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.letemps.ch/monde/chef-independantistes-hongkong-condamne-6-ans-prison |title = Le chef des indépendantistes de Hongkong condamné à 6 ans de prison |author =  |date = 2018-06-11 |publisher = 《{{Link-en|時報 (瑞士)|Le Temps|時報}}》 |language = fr |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723085905/https://www.letemps.ch/monde/chef-independantistes-hongkong-condamne-6-ans-prison |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.afpbb.com/articles/-/3178026 |script-title = ja:香港独立派の活動家に禁錮6年 2016年の暴動で有罪 |author =  |date = 2018-06-11 |publisher = [[法新社|法新社]] |language = ja |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190723085915/https://www.afpbb.com/articles/-/3178026 |archive-date = 2019-07-23 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。法官表明不想向社會釋出「能以暴力追求理念」的錯誤訊息<ref name="朱韻斐 01">{{Cite web |url = https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/198208/梁天琦案-何君堯指咎由自取刑期合適-有理想不代表有免死金牌 |title = 【梁天琦案】何君堯指咎由自取刑期合適　有理想不代表有免死金牌 |author = 朱韻斐 |date = 2018-06-12 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-07-23 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190724021313/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/198208/%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E6%A1%88-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E6%8C%87%E5%92%8E%E7%94%B1%E8%87%AA%E5%8F%96%E5%88%91%E6%9C%9F%E5%90%88%E9%81%A9-%E6%9C%89%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%89%E5%85%8D%E6%AD%BB%E9%87%91%E7%89%8C |archive-date = 2019-07-24 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，並指出暴動是集體的暴力行為，而參與暴動者是「咎由自取」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180611/bkn-20180611081614873-0611_00822_001.html |title = 旺暴案：梁天琦判監6年　盧建民囚7年　黃家駒